[[UCLA Medical Center]] |only appearance = [[Let's All Go to the Bar]] |seasons = '''[[Grey's Anatomy|GA]]:''' [[Season 16 (Grey's Anatomy)|16]] |portrayed by = [[Amanda Payton]] }} '''Daphne Lopez''' is a doctor who was considering a job at [[Pacific Northwest General Hospital]]. ==History== Daphne came into Pac-North looking for Alex to give her a walk-through. She was up in Seattle from UCLA and trying to decide between Pac-North and Seattle Pres for a new job. Owen offered to show her around, though she said they already had the edge because Seattle Pres can't afford her. At the end of the day, she told him she had a lot to think about. ==Career== She is an [[Emergency Medicine|Emergency medicine physician]]. She previously worked at UCLA, but was looking at hospitals in Seattle.
